    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then heat a large, wide-based, <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid, with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Trim the green stalk[s] off your<strong> aubergine[s] </strong>and chop into 4<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>wedges per person</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>aubergine wedges</strong> to the dish and cook for 2-3 min or until lightly browned</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
