    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Whilst the aubergine is browning, deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into chunks</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic </strong>open by squashing with the side of a knife and remove the skin</p>",
