    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, remove the aubergine from the oven and leave it to cool (lid on) for 4-5 min (this helps the flavours to develop), then give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>oven-baked Korean-style aubergine</strong></p>",
