      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>oven-baked Korean-style aubergine </strong>with the<strong> sticky rice </strong>and <strong>gochujang cucumber & edamame salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish the sticky rice with your <strong>black sesame seeds </strong>and drizzle any <strong>remaining gochujang sauce </strong>over the cucumber salad</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
